  "html": "\u003cdiv id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"\u003e\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003carticle\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cheader\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/header\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eThe killer of an Arizona man was sentenced to over 10 years behind bars after his victim spoke to the court via artificial intelligence in what could be the first-of-its-kind use of the technology. What do \u003cem\u003eyou\u003c/em\u003e think?\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://theonion.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Face-Black.jpg?w=200\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theonion.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Face-Black.jpg 200w, https://theonion.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Face-Black.jpg?resize=150,150 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e“That’s one hell of a surprise witness.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ccite\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eTim Roetman, Unemployed\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://theonion.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Face-Young-Woman.jpg?w=200\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theonion.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Face-Young-Woman.jpg 200w, https://theonion.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Face-Young-Woman.jpg?resize=150,150 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e“This is exactly why I’ve pre-recorded my response to being brutally murdered.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ccite\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eMichelle Wallis, Circus Historian\u003cbr/\u003e\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\u003chr/\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cfigure\u003e\u003cimg loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"200\" height=\"200\" src=\"https://theonion.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Face-Old-Man.jpg?w=200\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://theonion.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Face-Old-Man.jpg 200w, https://theonion.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Face-Old-Man.jpg?resize=150,150 150w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 200px) 100vw, 200px\"/\u003e\u003c/figure\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv\u003e\n\u003cblockquote\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e“That must have been hard to watch without trying to kill him again.”\u003c/p\u003e\n\u003ccite\u003e\u003cstrong\u003eAntonio Rossi, Law Proclaimer\u003c/strong\u003e\u003c/cite\u003e\u003c/blockquote\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/article\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cfigure\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cimg src=\"https://theonion.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/newsletter-paper-plane-icon.jpg\" alt=\"\"/\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/figure\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cdiv\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003ch3 id=\"h-like-a-vitamin-you-ingest-with-your-eyes-get-the-onion-newsletter\"\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003cstrong\u003eLike A Vitamin You Ingest With Your Eyes. Get The Onion Newsletter\u003c/strong\u003e.\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\u003c/h3\u003e\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n                \u003cdiv data-form-theme=\"gravity-